high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the bath tub, turn left, go forward to the sink counter.
Take the towel from the wall to the right.
Turn around with the bath tub to the left.
Put the towel in the bath tub.
Go forward, turn right, go forward to the sink counter to the left of the shower.
Take the towel from the wall.
Turn around, go forward to the bath tub, turn left, go forward to the sink counter, turn around.
Put the towel in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels in a bath tub.

high_descs: Walk to the sink counter in front of you and then take a step to your right.
Take the towel off of the ring hanging on the wall to your right.
Turn around.
Put the towel in the tub to your left.
Walk to the toilet then turn left and walk to the sink in front of you.
Take the towel off of the ring there too.
Go back to where you put the first towel
Put this towel next to the one in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels in the tub.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the sink.
Take the towel off the towel bar on the right.
Turn around.
Place the towel in the tub near the drain on the left side.
Turn right and walk to the other sink at the far wall.
Take the towel off of the towel rack to the right of the mirror.
Turn around and walk back to the bath tub.
Place the towel in the bath tub to the right of the first towel.
anns.task_desc: Place two towels in a bath tub.
